# lcod://tooling/array/filter_objects@0.1.0

Filter an array to keep only plain objects.

## Inputs

| Name | Type | Required | Description |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| `items` | array | No | Array potentially containing objects. |

## Outputs

| Name | Type | Description |
| --- | --- | --- |
| `items` | array | Filtered array containing only non-null objects. |
